36&|generic_scrap@,decl| $\RA$ |generic_scrap|\[G_2=G_1\,|force|\,D]
&generic formal part grows\cr
37&|generic_scrap@,proc| $\RA$ |proc|\[P_2=|indent|\,G\,|outdent|\,|force|\,P_1]
&generic formal part ends\cr
