47&|math@,colon@,decl| $\RA$ |decl|&block with name and \&{declare}\cr
&\qquad\[D_2=|force|\,|backup|\,\pd\,M\,\sp\,\pd\,C\,\sp\,|cancel|\,D_1]\cr
