&\qquad\[D=\pd\,M\,\pd\,F\,|indent|\,|force|\,R\,|indent|\,|force|]\cr
52&|math@,loop_scrap| $\RA$ |beginning|\[B=\pd\,M\,\pd\,\sp\,L]
&\&{loop} with \&{for} or \&{while}\cr
