55&|math@,stmt| $\RA$ |stmt|\[S_2=\pd\,M\,\pd\,S_1]&simple concatenation\cr
56&|math@,separate_scrap| $\RA$ |separate_scrap|\[S_2=\pd\,M\,\pd\,S_1]&in emergencies\cr
57&|math@,when_scrap@,math| $\RA$ |math|&\&{exit} \&{when} $x$;\cr
