&\&{for} $x$ \&{use} \dots\cr
59&|mod_scrap| $\RA$ |math|&module unlike a statement\cr
60&|mod_scrap@,semi| $\RA$ |stmt|\[S_2=M\,S_1\,|force|]
&module like a statement\cr
61&|new_scrap| $\RA$ |math|&\&{new} in allocator\cr
62&|not_scrap| $\RA$ |math|&\&{not} as `$\R$'\cr
63&|not_scrap@,in_scrap| $\RA$ |math|\[M=\.{\\notin}]&\&{not} \&{in} as `$\notin$'\cr
