&\qquad\[M_3=O\,|indent|\,M_1\,C_1\,M_2\,|outdent|\,C_2]\cr
67&|period| $\RA$ |math|&period in selected component\cr
68&|private_scrap| $\RA$ |decl|\[D=|force|\,|backup|\,P\,|force|]
&beginning of private part\cr
